                        <locus target="#">-</locus>
                        <desc>Drawings / decorations</desc>
                        <q>سجدة منذوبة</q>
                        <note>Mark indicating when a postration has to be done</note>
                     </decoNote>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d0">
                        <locus target="#">-</locus>
                        <desc>Drawings / decorations</desc>
                        <q>الجزؤ [...], نصف الجزؤ, ثمن</q>
                        <note>Marks for the aǧzā', their halves, and the eighths. The mark for the ǧuz' sometimes is inside a squared frame</note>
                     </decoNote>
